      "content": "\"let go and find peace in the emptiness\"... that sounds so quiet. almost beautiful in a way. but isn't it terrifying? to just stop? i feel like i've been fighting this heavy heaviness for years, trying to force the spark back, but it's like trying to breathe underwater. it's just so exhausting.",
